@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = PASTE_ADMIN_JWT_HERE
@trainerToken = PASTE_TRAINER_JWT_HERE

### 1) Login admin (skopiuj token do @adminToken)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@fitmanager.pl",
    "password": "Admin123"
}

### 2) Lista wszystkich userow
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 3) Lista tylko trenerow
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/trainers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4) Dodaj klienta
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "nowyklient@fitmanager.pl",
    "password": "Haslo123",
    "role": "CLIENT",
    "firstName": "Nowy",
    "lastName": "Klient",
    "phoneNumber": "600700800"
}

### 5) Dodaj trenera
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/trainers
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "nowytrener@fitmanager.pl",
    "password": "Trener123",
    "firstName": "Nowy",
    "lastName": "Trener",
    "phoneNumber": "700800900"
}

### 6) Edytuj usera (podmien ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/3
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Anna",
    "lastName": "Nowak-Zmieniona",
    "phoneNumber": "555000111"
}

### 7) Edytuj trenera (podmien ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/trainers/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Jan",
    "lastName": "Kowalski-Updated",
    "phoneNumber": "987000111"
}

### 8) Przypisz klienta do trenera (trainerId/clientId podmien)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/trainers/2/clients/3
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9) Lista podopiecznych trenera
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/trainers/2/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 10) Odpisz klienta od trenera
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/trainers/2/clients/3
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 11) Usun usera (podmien ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/3
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 12) Usun trenera (podmien ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/trainers/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 13) Login trener (skopiuj token do @trainerToken)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "trener@fitmanager.pl",
    "password": "Trener123"
}

### 14) Profil aktualnie zalogowanego usera (/api/me)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me
Authorization: Bearer {{trainerToken}}

### 15) Podopieczni zalogowanego trenera
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/trainer/me/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{trainerToken}}